Servicios</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Repositorio</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Pago M&oacute;vil</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Portal destinado al usuario final de facturas</p></li><li><p>Permite pagar facturas con Tarjetas de D&eacute;bito y Cr&eacute;dito</p></li><li><p>Ver transacciones realizadas con TC y TD</p></li></ul></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Commerce-Suite (Portal de Comercios)</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Portal destinado a los comercios</p></li><li><p>Contiene la interfaz web para usuarios de comercios</p><ul><li><p>Boca Web, Facturador Offline (biller-service) y vPOS</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Consume principalmente commerce-service y epos-service</p></li></ul></td><td><ul><li><p>Commerce-service</p></li></ul></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Portal de Directores</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Directores suben archivos y son compartidos con otros directores</p></li><li><p>Actas y Presentaciones</p></li></ul></td><td><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-s4-service\">S4-service</a> con archivos privados</p></li></ul></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Portal de Lealtad</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Portal para entidades</p></li><li><p>Permite definir y gestionar campa&ntilde;as de puntos</p></li></ul></td><td><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-loyalty-service\">Loyaly-service</a></p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-loyalty-portal\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-loyalty-portal</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Portal de Autenticaci&oacute;n</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Vistas para activar tu cuenta</p></li><li><p>Vistas para cambio de password</p></li><li><p>Vistas para olvid&eacute; mi password</p></li></ul></td><td><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-auth-service\">Auth-service</a></p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-auth-portal\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-auth-portal</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Portal de vPOS</p></td><td><ul><li><p>App similar a Paypal</p></li><li><p>Vistas donde las p&aacute;ginas de los comercios redirigen para que el usuario final ingrese y pague con su tarjeta</p></li></ul></td><td><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-vpos-service\">vPOS-service</a></p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-vpos-portal\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-vpos-portal</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>TPago</p></td><td><p /></td><td><ul><li><p>payment-link-service</p></li></ul></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><p><em>Ambientes con los que trabajamos en Bancard </em>&darr;</p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Ambientes en Bancard\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /><ac:link-body>Ambientes en Bancard</ac:link-body></ac:link><p> </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2794356818"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":190689049},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2794356818/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2794356818/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2794356818/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2794356818/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2794356818","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2794356818/Portales+de+Bancard","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2794356818","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2794356818","tinyui":"/x/UoCOpg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}